<appendix id="cha.ha.docupdates">
  <title>Documentation Updates</title>
  <para> This chapter lists content changes for this document since the
    release of &productnamereg; 11 SP3. </para>
  <para> This manual was updated on the following dates: </para>
  <!--list of xrefs, latest date sorted upmost-->
  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        <xref linkend="sec.ha.docupdates.sle12_ga" 
          xrefstyle="SectTitleOnPage"/>
      </para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>

  <sect1 id="sec.ha.docupdates.sle12_ga">
    <title>October, 2014 (Initial Release of &productname; 12)</title>

    <variablelist>
      <!--list of general issues that apply to all books-->
      <varlistentry id="vl.ha.docupdates.sle12_ga.general">
        <term>General</term>
        <listitem>
          <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
              <para> For quick and easy cluster setup, the former bootstrap
                scripts <filename>sleha-init</filename>,
                  <filename>sleha-join</filename>, and
                  <filename>sleha-remove</filename> has been renamed to
                  <filename>ha-cluster-init</filename>,
                  <filename>ha-cluster-join</filename>, and
                  <filename>ha-cluster-remove</filename>. The log file has
                been changed from
                  <filename>/var/log/sleha-bootstrap.log</filename> to
                  <filename>/var/log/ha-cluster-bootstrap.log</filename>
                (<ulink url="http://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=853772"/>).
              </para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>Replaced any occurance of <command>chkconfig</command> and 
              <command>rc*</command> commands with systemd equivalents 
               (<ulink url="http://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=853533"/>).</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>Used a consistent naming schema for cluster names, node names,
                constraints, contraints, and resources across the whole 
                documentation. See <xref linkend="app.naming"/>. (FATE#314938).</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>Removed &hbgui; and the references pointing to it 
                (FATE#312948, <ulink url="https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=853508"/>).</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>Replaced &ais; wth &corosync; (<ulink
                  url="https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=853507"/>,
                  <ulink
                  url="https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=853556"
                />).</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>Improve consistency of &crmshell; examples.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>Adapated new packages throughout the whole manual
                (FATE#314807).</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>Dropped list of resource agents in appendix. </para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>Splitted HA and HA Geo documentation into separate 
                documents (FATE#316121)</para>
            </listitem>
          </itemizedlist>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      
      <varlistentry>
        <term><xref linkend="cha.ha.concepts"/></term>
